title: ikidsislands IKS95R [Large Size] Magnetic Drawing Board for Toddlers, Color Magna Erasable Doodle Pad for Kids, Mess Free Coloring Write and Learn Creative Educational Toys for Girls & Boys (Red)
feature_bullets: [" ✔ SAFE & NON-TOXIC TODDLER LEARNING TOYS: Our magnetic doodle board is made ofBPA-free, Phthalate-free materials and has been tested in a USA government-approved lab, meets or exceeds U.S. ASTM-F963 toy safety standards, the test report is available for you"," ✔ FRIENDLY TO BOTH LEFT-HANDED & RIGHT-HANDED: We designed the magnetic pen on the top, unlike others put the pen on the right or left, our unique design will make doodling easier for both Left-Handed and Right-Handed, the stylus is tethered on a string which is a good length to draw all over the board while not being so long it gets in the way, we also designed the unique seal back panel to make it more durable, more comfortable when kids put it on their thigh,too"," ✔ 4 BIGGER STAMPS FOR SAFETY, CARVED ALPHABETS (A-Z) & NUMBERS (0-9) FOR MONTESSORI EDUCATIONAL: We designed the bigger magnet stamps than others, so it's not easy to be swallowed by toddlers, more safer, the 4 magnet shapes stay quite well in the frame, hard to fall off, we also carved the 26 Alphabets and 10 Numbers on the blue frame, so that your can made a game out of pointing out the letters, then trying to write them"," ✔ TRAVEL TOYS FOR TODDLER TRAVEL ACTIVITIES: There are 4 vivid color zones (blue, red, yellow, green) on the large colorful drawing area, the product dimension: 11.6 x 9.0 in, the drawing screen dimension: 6.7 x 4.3 in,the portable light weight sketch pad has great size for home, car rides, train trip, airplane trip and so on. It's also a great quiet toy that can keep the little one entertained or occupied during daycare, home, church, in flight, on the train or in the car"," ✔ IDEAL TODDLER GIFTS, MESS FREE, EASY TO ERASE & RESTART: Simply slide the eraser 1-2 times slowly, you can wipe out the screen, it's easy for toddlers to use the erasable etch pad, our drawing pad saves you from having crayons everywhere or having to clean up crayon marks off the floors and walls, hours of fun with No Mess, Ideal educational gifts for toddler girls & boys, best gifts for New Year, Valentines Day, Easter, Children's Day, Thanksgiving, Christmas, Xmas, Holiday, Birthday"]
